    <sect1 xml:id="sec.rac_installation">
        <title>安装 Oracle RAC</title>
        <para>以下部分介绍了如何执行 Oracle RAC 安装。</para>

        <sect2 xml:id="sec.grid_infra">
            <title>安装 Oracle Grid Infrastructure</title>

            <sect3 xml:id="sec.grid_prep">
                <title>准备步骤</title>
                <para>以非管理用户身份登录 &sls; 12 64位操作系统。 下载适用于 Linux x86-64 的 Oracle Database 12c Release 1 Grid
                    Infrastructure (12.1.0.2.0)。</para>
                <para>提取 <filename>grid.zip</filename> 并从 Grid ShipHome 运行安装程序 <command>'./runInstaller'</command> 。</para>
            </sect3>

            <sect3 xml:id="sec.grid_installation">
                <title>安装</title>
                <para>对于实际安装，请按照以下步骤操作：</para>
                <procedure>
                    <step>
                        <para>选择 <emphasis role="strong">Installation Option</emphasis>。</para>
                        <figure>
                            <title>Installation Option </title>
                            <mediaobject>
                                <imageobject role="fo">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-install-option.png" width="70%"
                                        format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                                <imageobject role="html">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-install-option.png" width="80%"
                                        format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                            </mediaobject>
                        </figure>
                        <para>选择 <emphasis role="strong">Install and Configure Oracle
                                Grid Infrastructure for a Cluster</emphasis> 选项，然后点击 <emphasis
                                role="strong">Next</emphasis> 继续。</para>
                    </step>
                    <step>
                        <para>下一步为 <emphasis role="strong">Cluster Type</emphasis>。</para>
                        <figure>
                            <title>Cluster Type</title>
                            <mediaobject>
                                <imageobject role="fo">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-cluster-type.png" width="70%"
                                        format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                                <imageobject role="html">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-cluster-type.png" width="80%"
                                        format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                            </mediaobject>
                        </figure>
                        <para>选择 <emphasis role="strong">Configure a Standard
                                Cluster</emphasis> 选项，然后点击 <emphasis role="strong"
                                >Next</emphasis> 继续。</para>
                    </step>
                    <step>
                        <para>下一步为 <emphasis role="strong">Installation Type</emphasis>。</para>
                        <figure>
                            <title>Installation Type </title>
                            <mediaobject>
                                <imageobject role="fo">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-install-type.png" width="70%"
                                        format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                                <imageobject role="html">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-install-type.png" width="80%"
                                        format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                            </mediaobject>
                        </figure>
                        <para>选择 <emphasis role="strong">Advanced
                                Installation</emphasis> 选项，然后点击 <emphasis role="strong"
                                >Next</emphasis> 继续。</para>
                    </step>
                    <step>
                        <para>下一步为 <emphasis role="strong">Product Languages</emphasis>。</para>
                        <figure>
                            <title>Product Languages</title>
                            <mediaobject>
                                <imageobject role="fo">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-product-language.png" width="70%"
                                        format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                                <imageobject role="html">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-product-language.png" width="80%"
                                        format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                            </mediaobject>
                        </figure>
                        <para>选择全部语言，然后点击 <emphasis role="strong"
                                >Next</emphasis> 继续。</para>
                    </step>
                    <step>
                        <para>填入要求的 <emphasis role="strong">Grid Plug and Play
                                Information</emphasis>。</para>
                        <figure>
                            <title>Grid Plug and Play Information</title>
                            <mediaobject>
                                <imageobject role="fo">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-grid-info.png" width="70%"
                                        format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                                <imageobject role="html">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-grid-info.png" width="80%"
                                        format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                            </mediaobject>
                        </figure>
                        <para>依照页面截图中显示的信息填写，然后点击
                                <emphasis role="strong">Next</emphasis> 继续。</para>
                        <para>有关GNS配置的更多详细信息，请参阅 <link
                                xlink:href="https://docs.oracle.com/database/121/CWLIN/toc.htm"
                            /> 上的 Oracle 官方文档</para>
                    </step>
                    <step>
                        <para>下一步为 <emphasis role="strong">Cluster Node
                            Information</emphasis>。</para>
                        <figure>
                            <title>Cluster Node Information </title>
                            <mediaobject>
                                <imageobject role="fo">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-cluster-node-info.png"
                                        width="70%" format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                                <imageobject role="html">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-cluster-node-info.png"
                                        width="80%" format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                            </mediaobject>
                        </figure>
                        <para>提供节点列表及其公共主机名和虚拟主机名，然后点击 <emphasis role="strong">Next</emphasis> 继续。</para>
                    </step>
                    <step>
                        <para>指定 <emphasis role="strong">Network Interface Usage</emphasis>。</para>
                        <figure>
                            <title>Network Interface Usage</title>
                            <mediaobject>
                                <imageobject role="fo">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-network-interface.png"
                                        width="70%" format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                                <imageobject role="html">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-network-interface.png"
                                        width="80%" format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                            </mediaobject>
                        </figure>
                        <para>提供 Oracle Grid 用于公共和专用流量的接口的详细信息，然后点击 <emphasis role="strong"
                                >Next</emphasis> 继续。</para>
                    </step>
                    <step>
                        <para>填入 <emphasis role="strong">Storage Option
                                Information</emphasis>。</para>
                        <figure>
                            <title>Storage Option Information</title>
                            <mediaobject>
                                <imageobject role="fo">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-storage-option.png" width="70%"
                                        format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                                <imageobject role="html">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-storage-option.png" width="80%"
                                        format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                            </mediaobject>
                        </figure>
                        <para>选择 <emphasis role="strong">Use Standard ASM for
                                storage</emphasis>，然后点击 <emphasis role="strong"
                                >Next</emphasis> 继续。</para>
                    </step>
                    <step>
                        <para>下一步为 <emphasis role="strong">Create ASM Disk
                            Group</emphasis>。</para>
                        <figure>
                            <title>Create AMS Disk Group</title>
                            <mediaobject>
                                <imageobject role="fo">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-asm-disk-group.png" width="70%"
                                        format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                                <imageobject role="html">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-asm-disk-group.png" width="80%"
                                        format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                            </mediaobject>
                        </figure>
                        <para>根据您的需要，创建 <emphasis role="strong"> ASM Disk
                                Group </emphasis>，然后点击 <emphasis role="strong"
                                >Next</emphasis> 继续。</para>
                    </step>
                    <step>
                        <para>指定 <emphasis role="strong">ASM Password</emphasis>。</para>
                        <figure>
                            <title>ASM Password</title>
                            <mediaobject>
                                <imageobject role="fo">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-asm-password.png" width="70%"
                                        format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                                <imageobject role="html">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-asm-password.png" width="80%"
                                        format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                            </mediaobject>
                        </figure>
                        <para>依照上面的页面截图填写 ASM 密码，然后点击
                                <emphasis role="strong">Next</emphasis> 继续。</para>
                    </step>
                    <step>
                        <para>定义 <emphasis role="strong">Failure Isolation
                                Support</emphasis>。</para>
                        <figure>
                            <title>Failure Isolation Support</title>
                            <mediaobject>
                                <imageobject role="fo">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-failure-isolation.png"
                                        width="70%" format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                                <imageobject role="html">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-failure-isolation.png"
                                        width="80%" format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                            </mediaobject>
                        </figure>
                        <para>选择 <emphasis role="strong">Do not use IPMI</emphasis>，然后点击 <emphasis role="strong">Next</emphasis> 继续。</para>
                    </step>
                    <step>
                        <para>指定 <emphasis role="strong">Management
                            Options</emphasis>。</para>
                        <figure>
                            <title>Management Options</title>
                            <mediaobject>
                                <imageobject role="fo">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-management-options.png"
                                        width="70%" format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                                <imageobject role="html">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-management-options.png"
                                        width="80%" format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                            </mediaobject>
                        </figure>
                        <para>根据您的需要选择或取消选择 <emphasis role="strong">Register
                                with EM</emphasis> 选项，然后点击  <emphasis role="strong">Next</emphasis> 继续。</para>
                    </step>
                    <step>
                        <para>下一步为 <emphasis role="">Privileged Operating System
                                Groups</emphasis>。</para>
                        <figure>
                            <title>Privileged Operating System Groups</title>
                            <mediaobject>
                                <imageobject role="fo">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-priviledged-osgroups.png"
                                        width="70%" format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                                <imageobject role="html">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-priviledged-osgroups.png"
                                        width="80%" format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                            </mediaobject>
                        </figure>
                        <para>操作系统组为默认选择。 点击 <emphasis
                                role="strong">Next</emphasis> 继续。</para>
                    </step>
                    <step>
                        <para>指定 <emphasis role="strong">Installation
                            Location</emphasis>。</para>
                        <figure>
                            <title>Installation Location</title>
                            <mediaobject>
                                <imageobject role="fo">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-install-location.png" width="70%"
                                        format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                                <imageobject role="html">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-install-location.png" width="80%"
                                        format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                            </mediaobject>
                        </figure>
                        <para>填入 <emphasis role="strong">Oracle base</emphasis> 和 
                                <emphasis role="strong">Software location</emphasis>，然后点击
                                <emphasis role="strong">Next</emphasis> 继续。</para>
                    </step>
                    <step>
                        <para>创建 <emphasis role="strong">Inventory</emphasis>。</para>
                        <figure>
                            <title>Create Inventory</title>
                            <mediaobject>
                                <imageobject role="fo">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-create-inventory.png" width="70%"
                                        format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                                <imageobject role="html">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-create-inventory.png" width="80%"
                                        format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                            </mediaobject>
                        </figure>
                        <para>如果这是您在此主机上的第一次安装，请指定安装元数据文件的目录。点击 <emphasis role="strong"
                                >Next</emphasis> 继续。</para>
                    </step>
                    <step>
                        <para>下一步为 <emphasis role="strong">Root Script Execution
                                Configuration</emphasis>。</para>
                        <figure>
                            <title>Root Script Execution Configuration</title>
                            <mediaobject>
                                <imageobject role="fo">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-root-script.png" width="70%"
                                        format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                                <imageobject role="html">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-root-script.png" width="80%"
                                        format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                            </mediaobject>
                        </figure>
                        <para>配置软件时，您需要以 <emphasis role="strong">root</emphasis> 用户身份执行一些操作。 选择如上所示的选项。 这样 <emphasis role="strong">Installer</emphasis> 将自动执行这些操作。 填写 <emphasis role="strong">root</emphasis> 用户的密码。点击 <emphasis
                                role="strong">Next</emphasis> 继续。</para>
                    </step>
                    <step>
                        <para>下一步为 <emphasis role="strong">Prerequisite
                            Check</emphasis>。</para>
                        <figure>
                            <title>Prerequisite Checks 1</title>
                            <mediaobject>
                                <imageobject role="fo">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-prerequis-checks-1.png"
                                        width="70%" format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                                <imageobject role="html">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-prerequis-checks-1.png"
                                        width="80%" format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                            </mediaobject>
                        </figure>
                        <para>如上图所示，执行先决条件检查。 点击 <emphasis role="strong">Fix&amp;Check Again</emphasis> 以重新检查系统。</para>
                        <figure>
                            <title>Prerequisite Checks 2</title>
                            <mediaobject>
                                <imageobject role="fo">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-prerequis-checks-2.png"
                                        width="70%" format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                                <imageobject role="html">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-prerequis-checks-2.png"
                                        width="80%" format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                            </mediaobject>
                        </figure>
                        <para>按照提示操作，在每个节点上以 <emphasis
                                role="strong">root</emphasis> 身份手动运行 fixup 脚本。点击 <emphasis
                                role="strong">OK</emphasis>。</para>
                        <screen><emphasis role="red">c2n1:/home #</emphasis> /tmp/CVU_12.1.0.2.0_oracle/runfixup.sh
All Fix-up operations were completed successfully.
<emphasis role="red">c2n1:/home #</emphasis></screen>
                        <figure>
                            <title>Prerequisite Checks 3</title>
                            <mediaobject>
                                <imageobject role="fo">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-prerequis-checks-3.png"
                                        width="70%" format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                                <imageobject role="html">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-prerequis-checks-3.png"
                                        width="80%" format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                            </mediaobject>
                        </figure>
                        <para>在 <emphasis role="strong">Fixup Result</emphasis> 选项卡上，选中 <emphasis role="strong">Ignore All</emphasis> 选项。 点击
                                <emphasis role="strong">Next</emphasis> 继续。</para>
                    </step>
                    <step>
                        <para>查看 <emphasis role="strong">Summary</emphasis>。</para>
                        <figure>
                            <title>Summary</title>
                            <mediaobject>
                                <imageobject role="fo">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-summary.png" width="70%"
                                        format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                                <imageobject role="html">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-summary.png" width="80%"
                                        format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                            </mediaobject>
                        </figure>
                        <para>查看安装 <emphasis role="strong">Summary</emphasis>，如上所示。 如果一切正确，点击 <emphasis role="strong"
                                >Install</emphasis> 继续。</para>
                    </step>
                    <step>
                        <para>安装产品。</para>
                        <figure>
                            <title>Install Product - Progress</title>
