        <sect2 xml:id="sec.database">
            <title>安装 Oracle 数据库</title>

            <sect3 xml:id="sec.db_install_prep">
                <title>准备步骤</title>
                <para>以非管理员用户身份登录 &sls; 12 64位操作系统。 下载适用于 Linux x86-64 的Oracle Database 12c Release 1 (12.1.0.2.0)。</para>
                <para>提取 <filename>grid.zip</filename> 并从 Database ShipHome 运行安装程序 <command>'./runInstaller'</command> 。</para>
            </sect3>

            <sect3 xml:id="sec.db_installation">
                <title>安装</title>
                <para>对于实际安装，请按照以下步骤操作：</para>
                <procedure>
                    <step>
                        <para>选择 <emphasis role="strong">Configure Security
                            Updates</emphasis></para>
                        <figure>
                            <title>Configure Security Updates </title>
                            <mediaobject>
                                <imageobject role="fo">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-security-updates.png" width="70%"
                                        format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                                <imageobject role="html">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-security-updates.png" width="80%"
                                        format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                            </mediaobject>
                        </figure>
                        <para>提供您的电子邮件地址以了解安全问题，然后点击 <emphasis role="strong">Next</emphasis> 继续。</para>
                    </step>
                    <step>
                        <para>下一步为 <emphasis role="strong">Installation Option</emphasis>。</para>
                        <figure>
                            <title>Installation Option</title>
                            <mediaobject>
                                <imageobject role="fo">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-install-option-2.png" width="70%"
                                        format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                                <imageobject role="html">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-install-option-2.png" width="80%"
                                        format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                            </mediaobject>
                        </figure>
                        <para>选择 <emphasis>Install database software only</emphasis>，然后点击 <emphasis>Next</emphasis> 继续。</para>
                    </step>
                    <step>
                        <para>下一步为 <emphasis role="strong">Grid Installation
                            Options</emphasis>。</para>
                        <figure>
                            <title>Grid Installation Options</title>
                            <mediaobject>
                                <imageobject role="fo">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-grid-install.png" width="70%"
                                        format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                                <imageobject role="html">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-grid-install.png" width="80%"
                                        format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                            </mediaobject>
                        </figure>
                        <para>选择 <emphasis role="strong">Oracle Real Application
                                Clusters database installation</emphasis>，然后点击 <emphasis
                                role="strong">Next</emphasis> 继续。</para>
                    </step>
                    <step>
                        <para>转到 <emphasis role="strong">Nodes Selection</emphasis> 以从节点列表中进行选择节点。</para>
                        <figure>
                            <title>Nodes Selection</title>
                            <mediaobject>
                                <imageobject role="fo">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-list-nodes.png" width="70%"
                                        format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                                <imageobject role="html">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-list-nodes.png" width="80%"
                                        format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                            </mediaobject>
                        </figure>
                        <para>选择群集中的所有节点，然后点击 <emphasis role="strong"
                                >Next</emphasis> 继续。</para>
                    </step>
                    <step>
                        <para>下一步为 <emphasis role="strong">Product Languages</emphasis>。</para>
                        <figure>
                            <title>Product Languages</title>
                            <mediaobject>
                                <imageobject role="fo">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-product-language-2.png"
                                        width="70%" format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                                <imageobject role="html">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-product-language-2.png"
                                        width="80%" format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                            </mediaobject>
                        </figure>
                        <para>选择所有语言，然后点击 <emphasis role="strong"
                                >Next</emphasis> 继续。</para>
                    </step>
                    <step>
                        <para>选择 <emphasis role="strong">Database Edition</emphasis>。</para>
                        <figure>
                            <title>Database Edition</title>
                            <mediaobject>
                                <imageobject role="fo">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-database-edition.png" width="70%"
                                        format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                                <imageobject role="html">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-database-edition.png" width="80%"
                                        format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                            </mediaobject>
                        </figure>
                        <para>选择 <emphasis role="strong">Enterprise
                                Edition</emphasis>，然后点击 <emphasis role="strong"
                                >Next</emphasis> 继续。</para>
                    </step>
                    <step>
                        <para>指定 <emphasis role="strong">Installation
                            Location</emphasis>。</para>
                        <figure>
                            <title>Installation Location</title>
                            <mediaobject>
                                <imageobject role="fo">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-install-location-2.png"
                                        width="70%" format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                                <imageobject role="html">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-install-location-2.png"
                                        width="80%" format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                            </mediaobject>
                        </figure>
                        <para>如上所示，填入 <emphasis role="strong">Oracle base</emphasis> 和 
                                <emphasis role="strong">Software location</emphasis>。
                            然后，点击 <emphasis role="strong">Next</emphasis> 继续。</para>
                    </step>
                    <step>
                        <para>定义特权 <emphasis role="strong">Operating System
                                Groups</emphasis>。</para>
                        <figure>
                            <title>Operating System Groups</title>
                            <mediaobject>
                                <imageobject role="fo">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-priviledged-osgroups-2.png"
                                        width="70%" format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                                <imageobject role="html">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-priviledged-osgroups-2.png"
                                        width="80%" format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                            </mediaobject>
                        </figure>
                        <para>特权操作系统组为默认选择。 点击
                                <emphasis role="strong">Next</emphasis> 继续。</para>
                    </step>
                    <step>
                        <para>执行 <emphasis role="strong">Prerequisite Checks
                            </emphasis>。</para>
                        <figure>
                            <title>Prerequisite Checks</title>
                            <mediaobject>
                                <imageobject role="fo">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-prerequis-checks-1-1.png"
                                        width="70%" format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                                <imageobject role="html">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-prerequis-checks-1-1.png"
                                        width="80%" format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                            </mediaobject>
                        </figure>
                        <para>如上图所示，执行先决条件检查，重新检查系统。点击 <emphasis role="strong">Fix&amp;Check Again</emphasis> 继续。</para>
                        <figure>
                            <title>Fixup Script</title>
                            <mediaobject>
                                <imageobject role="fo">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-prerequis-checks-2-2.png"
                                        width="70%" format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                                <imageobject role="html">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-prerequis-checks-2-2.png"
                                        width="80%" format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                            </mediaobject>
                        </figure>
                        <para>按照提示操作，在每个节点上以 <quote>root</quote> 身份手动运行 fixup 脚本。点击 <emphasis
                                role="strong">OK</emphasis>。</para>
                        <para>您应该看到以下输出：</para>
                        <screen><emphasis role="red">c2n1 ~ #:</emphasis> /tmp/CVU_12.1.0.2.0_oracle/runfixup.sh
All Fix-up operations were completed successfully.</screen>
                        <para>在此处检查 <emphasis role="strong">Fixup Results</emphasis>：</para>
                        <figure>
                            <title>Fixup Results</title>
                            <mediaobject>
                                <imageobject role="fo">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-prerequis-checks-3-3.png"
                                        width="70%" format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                                <imageobject role="html">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-prerequis-checks-3-3.png"
                                        width="80%" format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                            </mediaobject>
                        </figure>
                        <para>在此处检查 <emphasis role="strong">Verification Results</emphasis>：</para>
                        <figure>
                            <title>Verification Results</title>
                            <mediaobject>
                                <imageobject role="fo">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-prerequis-checks-3.png"
                                        width="70%" format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                                <imageobject role="html">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-prerequis-checks-3.png"
                                        width="80%" format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                            </mediaobject>
                        </figure>
                        <para>选择 <emphasis role="strong">Ignore All</emphasis>，然后
                            点击 <emphasis role="strong">Next</emphasis> 继续。</para>
                    </step>
                    <step>
                        <para>查看 <emphasis role="strong">Summary</emphasis>。</para>
                        <figure>
                            <title>Summary</title>
                            <mediaobject>
                                <imageobject role="fo">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-summary-2.png" width="70%"
                                        format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                                <imageobject role="html">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-summary-2.png" width="80%"
                                        format="PNG"/>
                                </imageobject>
                            </mediaobject>
                        </figure>
                        <para>如果您看到如上所示的安装摘要，点击 <emphasis
                                role="strong">Install</emphasis> 继续。</para>
                    </step>
                    <step>
                        <para>下一步为 <emphasis role="strong">Install Product</emphasis>。</para>
                        <figure>
                            <title>Install Product</title>
                            <mediaobject>
                                <imageobject role="fo">
                                    <imagedata fileref="oracle-rac-install-product-loading.png"
                                        width="70%" format="PNG"/>
